::DarkMouse::
"You want me...a...to be your partner?"
She just stood there for a moment with a shocked expresion on her face.
"Uh, yes, sure, I'd be honored commander. Partners it is."
She just held her breath for a moment. She couldn't believe that in her 
wildest dreams a high ranking commander like Scorponok would ever ask to be 
partered up with a lowly mouse like herself.
"Thank you commander." she said in a high almost a squeeky voice.
She turned around and put her back to him for a bit.  Her face plates were 
turning a deep red and she didn't want him to see it.

Scorponok/Oinker


Scorponok looked at Darkmouse. "Well, I need to set up the lab. If
you
can, I would like to Set these machines up so that I can run a few
things if megatron wants me too. Also later I'm going to need a few
Table's set up so that if I have to reprogram any other bots I can do
so. But, I have one question for you, Will you be my Partner? I could
use somebody to watch my back and from the work I seen you do, You
could use someone to watch yours." But of corse that wasn't the only
reason why Scorponok wanted to be parterns, He wanted to be partners
so he could be close to her
